# Upstream Tracking

This repository was forked from
[**tailwind-nextjs-starter-blog**](https://github.com/timlrx/tailwind-nextjs-starter-blog)
by Timothy Lin (timlrx).

The original commit history (Tim's years of upstream development) has been
rewritten into a single root commit so this repo presents as a standalone
project. Tim's history remains fully accessible via the `upstream` remote
and on his original repo.

